Anonymous Inner Class;
----------------------
1.A Class without any name;
2.we use Anonymous Inner class with abstract class & interface

syntax: 
ClassName reference variable=new ClassName(){
//override abstract methods
};
***********************************************************
Lambda Expressions:
-------------------
1.Lambda Expressions is a small block of code which is use to implement 
functional interface
2.Marker interface is an Empty interface without any abstract Methods.
3.Functional Interface is an Interface with only 1 abstract method.


syntax:
InterfaceName reference variable=()-> {
override the abstract methods ->only implementation

};